<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="11" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1438,151,1106]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,318,383,409]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Remarks.</emphasis>
The two specimens examined match the features given in the original description. The original description further details the 
<typeStatus box="[505,555,422,448]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">type</typeStatus>
localities. The specimen from Silhouette was collected in the forest above Mare aux Cochons. The original description does not list the number of specimens collected from 
<collectingCountry box="[1360,1433,461,487]" name="India" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Mahé</collectingCountry>
. However, Distant seemed to have at least two specimens as he provides details of two different localities: Cascade Estate, 
<quantity box="[351,526,538,564]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.7432" metricValueMax="3.048" metricValueMin="2.4384" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" unit="ft" value="900.0" valueMax="1000.0" valueMin="800.0">800–1000 feet</quantity>
and over; high forest behind Trois Frères, 
<quantity box="[1052,1247,538,564]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.334" metricValueMax="6.096" metricValueMin="4.572" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" unit="ft" value="1750.0" valueMax="2000.0" valueMin="1500.0">1500–2000 feet</quantity>
. We could only locate one specimen from 
<collectingCountry box="[485,555,577,603]" name="India" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Mahé</collectingCountry>
in the 
<collectionCode box="[646,742,577,603]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">BMNH</collectionCode>
. Because the original description does not mention the designation of a 
<typeStatus box="[349,455,616,642]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">holotype</typeStatus>
, these specimens are regarded as 
<typeStatus box="[856,963,616,642]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">syntypes</typeStatus>
. The specimen from Silhouette labelled 
<typeStatus box="[151,212,654,680]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Type</typeStatus>
, H.T., is hereby designated as 
<typeStatus box="[568,675,654,680]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">lectotype</typeStatus>
to provide a diagnostic reference for the species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
